devdoc.title: DelegatedWalletManager Contract

addWallet(address).notice: Adds a wallet to the account list.

contains(address,address).notice: Shows if a wallet exists in the wallet list from a given account.

createWallet(address,address[]).notice: Adds a wallet to the account list.

getWallets(address).notice: Fetches a wallet list from a given account.

index(address,uint256).notice: Fetches the wallet at index 'i' from the 'account' wallet list

indexOf(address,address).notice: Fetches the index of a given 'wallet' from a given 'account' wallet list

removeWallet(address).notice: Removes a wallet from the account list.

totalWallets(address).notice: Fetches a how many wallets are in the list from a given account.
